<table  border=0 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=0 awidth=100%><a name=100161274774978></a><form action=http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/strategy/mrate.pl name=f100161274774978><tr><td id=headerrow><a id=sj href=classes.html?class=12&mid=100161274774978>RE: Money problems</a> <a id=fs8 href=classes.html?class=12&mid=100161274774978#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <span id= >Anonymous</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Thu, Sep 27th 1:45 PM 2001</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Default<span id=notbold>[2.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>I would advise going to South Karana.&nbsp;&nbsp;Kill the centaurs that con blue and white to ya, they drop good money usually, armor and gems.  or Kill the Gnolls at the spires.  You can kill treants, but then you get over loaded with gold instead of plat.  Gnolls are probably the fastest money there, but the spires are often very crowded.  The gnolls drop fine steel and other stuff.<br><br>Also at 30th you might beable to find a group in Rathe (sp?) mountains to kill hill giants with.  your DD's will be resisted a lot though unless you can get a debuff to stick first.  Make sure you get a good group there though, at 30th, those giants will drop ya fast if the group is too small.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
